@jreback : That's too bad.  LGTM.

FYI: The bullet point is a little weird in #6581 for that one.  On a separate note, could you also add a note regarding the `convert_objects` discussion we're having for the top bullet in `0.17.0`?
@gfyoung yep I completely reverted, but if you want to follow up with some of the cosmetic changes you did would be ok too.
